<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/materialize/1.0.0/css/materialize.min.css">
    
    <title>Cyst Detection</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            /* max-width: 800px; */
            /* margin: 30px auto; */
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h4 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .file-upload {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 200px;
            height: 50px;
        }
        .file-upload input.upload {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        .file-upload .file-cta {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #2196F3;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .file-upload .file-cta:hover {
            background: #0d8bf0;
        }
        .scissor-top {
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 70px;
            height: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            border-left: 1px solid #000;
            border-top-left-radius: 5px;
            border-top-right-radius: 5px;
        }
        .scissor-bottom {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 70px;
            height: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            border-left: 1px solid #000;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
        }
        .scissor-left {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: -10px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            height: 70px;
            width: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            border-left: 1px solid #000;
            border-top-left-radius: 5px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 5px;
        }
        .scissor-right {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            right: -10px;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            height: 70px;
            width: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #000;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
            border-right: 1px solid #000;
            border-top-right-radius: 5px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;
        }
        .image-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .img-responsive {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .file-path-wrapper {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .download-button {
            text-align: center;
            margin:auto;
        }
        .instructions {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .instructions h4 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .instructions p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .how-it-works-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .circle-section {
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .how-it-works-content-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .icons {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            flex: 1;
        }
        .icons img {
            max-width: 80px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h5 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .results-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .results-heading {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .results-content {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }

          /* Header styles */
          .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        .footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            /* position: fixed; */
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .spinner {
            display: none;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        .loader {
            border: 6px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 6px solid #3498db;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            animation: spin 2s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
      <header class="header" style="color:#fff;">
        <h5 style="color:#fff;">Cyst Detection Tool</h5>
    </header>
      <div class="container-fluid how-it-works-container">
        <h5 class="results-heading">How to Use Cyst Detection:</h5>
        <div class="row how-it-works-content-container">
            <div class="col-md-3 icons">
                <img class="icon_rep img-fluid" src="/images/Post Image.svg" alt="" />
                <h5>Choose OCT Image</h5>
                <p>Click on Choose File button</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 icons">
                <img class="icon_rep img-fluid" src="/images/Resume Icon.svg" alt="" />
                <h5>Upload</h5>
                <p>Click on Submit button to upload Image</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 icons">
                <img class="icon_rep img-fluid" src="images/Profile Icon.svg" alt="" />
                <h5>Get Output Image</h5>
                <p>The tool will identify the cysts in the image and display the segmented Image</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
      
        <h5 style="text-align: center;" class="results-heading">Detect Cysts with Precision</h5>
        <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="file-upload">
                <div class="file-cta">
                    <span>Choose File</span>
                    <input name="myimage" class="upload" type="file">
                </div>
                <div class="scissor-top"></div>
                <div class="scissor-bottom"></div>
                <div class="scissor-left"></div>
                <div class="scissor-right"></div>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn download-button" style="margin-top: 20px; align-items:center; justify-content: center; display: flex;">Submit</button>
        </form>
        <div class="spinner" id="spinner">
          <div class="loader"></div>
      </div>
        <div class="image-container">
            <h5>Original Image</h5>
            <img src="/uploads/test.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Uploaded Image">
            <h5>Segmented Image</h5>
            <img src="/pyimages/test.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Processed Image">
        </div>
        <div class="download-button">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-download">
                <a href="<%=typeof file4 != 'undefined' ? file4 : ''  %>" style="color: white;" download>Download</a>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="container-fluid results-section">
          <h5 class="results-heading">Results Interpretation:</h5>
          <div class="results-content">
              <li>
                  After the image is processed, the segmented image will display the identified cysts. The segmented image represents areas within the original image where cysts have been detected.
              </li>
              <li>
                  Users should understand that the segmented image is a visual representation highlighting potential cyst locations. It aids in identifying the regions of interest and assists in further analysis or diagnosis by healthcare professionals.
              </li>
              <li>
                  It's essential to note that while the tool identifies these regions, further medical assessment by a qualified professional is recommended for accurate diagnosis and treatment planning.
              </li>
          </div>
      </div>
      <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Cyst Detection Tool. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
    </div>
    <script>
      // Function to show the spinner
      function showSpinner() {
          document.getElementById('spinner').style.display = 'flex';
      }

      // Function to hide the spinner
      function hideSpinner() {
          document.getElementById('spinner').style.display = 'none';
      }

      // Add event listener to the form submission
      document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function() {
          showSpinner(); // Show the spinner when the form is submitted
      });

